Title: Our Town
Plot: After several disappearances in a small town, Mulder and Scully investigate and find hundreds of human bones in the river. They discover that the man behind the town's main source of wealth, a chicken processing plant, has found a way to prolong his life through cannibalism.
GuestStars: Gary Grubbs, John Milford, Caroline Kava, Robin Mossley, Timothy Webber, Hrothgar Mathews, Gabrielle Miller, John MacLaren, Robert Moloney, Carrie Cain Sparks
